<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Claudius_I-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z-Claudius_I&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Claudius I&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Claudius I&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Claudius_I-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z"><span class="mw-headline" id="Claudius_I"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Claudius_I-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z"></span>Claudius I<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Claudius_I-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Roman_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Claudius I"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Claudius_I-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z","replies":["c-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z-Claudius_I"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z-Claudius_I","timestamp":"2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__1__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__1__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Claudius_I-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z-Claudius_I&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Claudius I&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Claudius I&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z-Claudius_I"></span>I have restored the common names of some emperors. <i>Claudius I</i> is rare and unnecessary; if the use of <i>Claudius II</i> causes confusion, the right solution is to move him to <a href="/wiki/Claudius_Gothicus" title="Claudius Gothicus">Claudius Gothicus</a>. <a href="/wiki/User:Pmanderson" title="User:Pmanderson">Septentrionalis</a> <small><a href="/wiki/User_talk:Pmanderson" title="User talk:Pmanderson">PMAnderson</a></small> 17:10, 15 July 2008 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z-Claudius_I"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z","author":"Pmanderson","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z-Claudius_I","replies":[],"displayName":"Septentrionalis"}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Pmanderson-2008-07-15T17:10:00.000Z-Claudius_I"></span>
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Pmanderson-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Lucius_Verus-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Pmanderson-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z-Lucius_Verus&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Lucius Verus&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Lucius Verus&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Lucius_Verus-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z"><span class="mw-headline" id="Lucius_Verus"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Lucius_Verus-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z"></span>Lucius Verus<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Lucius_Verus-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Roman_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Lucius Verus"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Pmanderson-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Lucius_Verus-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z","replies":["c-Pmanderson-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z-Lucius_Verus"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Pmanderson-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z-Lucius_Verus","timestamp":"2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__1__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__1__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Pmanderson-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Lucius_Verus-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Pmanderson-2008-08-27T21:28:00.000Z-Lucius_Verus&quot;],&quot;