<p><a href="/wiki/Ulpia_Severina" title="Ulpia Severina"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-*Treker-2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z-Ulpia_and_Eudokia"></span>Ulpia Severina</a> seems to have actually ruled in her own right, while <a href="/wiki/Eudokia_Makrembolitissa" title="Eudokia Makrembolitissa">Eudokia Makrembolitissa</a>'s article doesn't mention any such thing. Why does Ulpia need to be removed but Eudokia not?<a href="/wiki/User:*Treker" class="mw-redirect" title="User:*Treker">★Trekker</a> (<a href="/wiki/User_talk:*Treker" class="mw-redirect" title="User talk:*Treker">talk</a>) 12:52, 12 November 2021 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-*Treker-2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z-Ulpia_and_Eudokia"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z","author":"*Treker","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-*Treker-2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z-Ulpia_and_Eudokia","replies":["c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z"],"displayName":"\u2605Trekker"}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-*Treker-2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z-Ulpia_and_Eudokia"></span>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z"></span>Eudokia's article is incomplete then. Though it's not universal (neither are some of the emperors included), there are several published lists of Byzantine monarchs and reference works (including the ODB) that include Eudokia as empress regnant. Certain Byzantine sources (such as the <i><a href="/wiki/Mutinensis_gr._122" title="Mutinensis gr. 122">Mutinensis gr. 122</a></i>) appear to include her as well. I agree that Ulpia Severina ought to also count but unless there are scholarly sources that consider her empress regnant I don't think we can include her. If those sources exist it isn't a problem. <a href="/wiki/User:Ichthyovenator" title="User:Ichthyovenator">Ichthyovenator</a> (<a href="/wiki/User_talk:Ichthyovenator" title="User talk:Ichthyovenator">talk</a>) 14:18, 12 November 2021 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z","author":"Ichthyovenator","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z","replies":["c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:47:00.000Z-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-12T12:52:00.000Z"></span>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:47:00.000Z-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z"></span>As a sidenote I've rectified Eudokia's article so that it mentions this. <a href="/wiki/User:Ichthyovenator" title="User:Ichthyovenator">Ichthyovenator</a> (<a href="/wiki/User_talk:Ichthyovenator" title="User talk:Ichthyovenator">talk</a>) 14:47, 12 November 2021 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:47:00.000Z-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2021-11-12T14:47:00.000Z","author":"Ichthyovenator","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:47:00.000Z-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:47:00.000Z-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-12T14:18:00.000Z"></span></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Sophia_(empress)-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z-Sophia_(empress)&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Sophia (empress)&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Sophia (empress)&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Sophia_(empress)-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z"><span id="Sophia_.28empress.29"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Sophia_(empress)"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Sophia_(empress)-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z"></span>Sophia (empress)<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Sophia_(empress)-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Roman_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Sophia (empress)"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Sophia_(empress)-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z","replies":["c-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z-Sophia_(empress)"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-16T16:52:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z","timestamp":"2021-11-16T16:52:00.000Z"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__2__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Sophia_(empress)-2021-11-16T16:07:00.0