<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z-Sophia_(empress)"></span>The category <a href="/w/index.php?title=Category:Byzantine_Empresses_regnant&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Category:Byzantine Empresses regnant (page does not exist)">Category:Byzantine Empresses regnant</a> was <a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Sophia_(empress)&amp;diff=1055386940&amp;oldid=1052391110">added to Sophia's article recently</a>. Is there any basis for the addition?<a href="/wiki/User:*Treker" class="mw-redirect" title="User:*Treker">★Trekker</a> (<a href="/wiki/User_talk:*Treker" class="mw-redirect" title="User talk:*Treker">talk</a>) 16:07, 16 November 2021 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z-Sophia_(empress)"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z","author":"*Treker","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z-Sophia_(empress)","replies":["c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-16T16:52:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z"],"displayName":"\u2605Trekker"}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z-Sophia_(empress)"></span>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-16T16:52:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z"></span>She was added there by the same person who added her to this template - there is considerable basis in WP:RS for calling Theodora and Eudokia empresses regnant, I don't think there is for Sophia so it constitutes <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:OR" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:OR">WP:OR</a> add her. I've removed her from the category. <a href="/wiki/User:Ichthyovenator" title="User:Ichthyovenator">Ichthyovenator</a> (<a href="/wiki/User_talk:Ichthyovenator" title="User talk:Ichthyovenator">talk</a>) 16:52, 16 November 2021 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-16T16:52:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2021-11-16T16:52:00.000Z","author":"Ichthyovenator","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-16T16:52:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Ichthyovenator-2021-11-16T16:52:00.000Z-*Treker-2021-11-16T16:07:00.000Z"></span></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_\&quot;junior_co-emperors\&quot;?-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_\&quot;junior_co-emperors\&quot;?&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Shouldn't Diadumenian and Philip II count as \&quot;junior co-emperors\&quot;?&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Shouldn't Diadumenian and Philip II count as \&quot;junior co-emperors\&quot;?&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Shouldn&#039;t_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_&quot;junior_co-emperors&quot;?-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z"><span id="Shouldn.27t_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_.22junior_co-emperors.22.3F"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_&quot;junior_co-emperors&quot;?"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_&quot;junior_co-emperors&quot;?-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z"></span>Shouldn't Diadumenian and Philip II count as "junior co-emperors"?<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_&quot;junior_co-emperors&quot;?-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Roman_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Shouldn&#039;t Diadumenian and Philip II count as &quot;junior co-emperors&quot;?"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_\"junior_co-emperors\"?-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z","replies":["c-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_\"junior_co-emperors\"?"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Ichthyovenator-2022-01-17T00:58:00.000Z-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z","timestamp":"2022-01-17T00:58:00.000Z"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__2__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_\&quot;junior_co-emperors\&quot;?-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_\&quot;junior_co-emperors\&quot;?&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Shouldn't Diadumenian and Philip II count as \&quot;junior co-emperors\&quot;?&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Shouldn't Diadumenian and Philip II count as \&quot;junior co-emperors\&quot;?&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_&quot;junior_co-emperors&quot;?"></span>A random thought I had. <a href="/wiki/User:Tintero21" title="User:Tintero21">Tintero21</a> (<a href="/wiki/User_talk:Tintero21" title="User talk:Tintero21">talk</a>) 00:48, 17 January 2022 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_&quot;junior_co-emperors&quot;?"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z","author":"Tintero21","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_\"junior_co-emperors\"?","replies":["c-Ichthyovenator-2022-01-17T00:58:00.000Z-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z-Shouldn't_Diadumenian_and_Philip_II_count_as_&quot;junior_co-emperors&quot;?"></span>
</p>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Ichthyovenator-2022-01-17T00:58:00.000Z-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z"></span>Yes they should but there seems to be a bit of a difference in how scholars of ancient Rome and Byzantium treat co-emperors; Diadumenian and Philip II (as well as some of the other clearly junior rulers) are counted among the other emperors in a lot of sources whereas Byzantine co-emperors typically aren't. Since we follow this in the list I think we should do so here as well. It's inconsistent but what can you do. <a href="/wiki/User:Ichthyovenator" title="User:Ichthyovenator">Ichthyovenator</a> (<a href="/wiki/User_talk:Ichthyovenator" title="User talk:Ichthyovenator">talk</a>) 00:58, 17 January 2022 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Ichthyovenator-2022-01-17T00:58:00.000Z-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2022-01-17T00:58:00.000Z","author":"Ichthyovenator","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Ichthyovenator-2022-01-17T00:58:00.000Z-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Ichthyovenator-2022-01-17T00:58:00.000Z-Tintero21-2022-01-17T00:48:00.000Z"></span></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-212.129.85.83-20221222185600&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022-20221222185600&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-212.129.85.83-20221222185600-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Semi-protected edit request on 22 December 2022&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Semi-protected edit request on 22 December 2022&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022-20221222185600"><span class="mw-headline" id="Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022-20221222185600"></span>Semi-protected edit request on 22 December 2022<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022-20221222185600"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Template_talk:Roman_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Semi-protected edit request on 22 December 2022"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-212.129.85.83-20221222185600","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022-20221222185600","replies":["c-212.129.85.83-20221222185600-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Asartea-20221226142200-212.129.85.83-20221222185600","timestamp":"20221226142200"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__2__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-212.129.85.83-20221222185600&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022-20221222185600&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-212.129.85.83-20221222185600-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Semi-protected edit request on 22 December 2022&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Semi-protected edit request on 22 December 2022&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-212.129.85.83-20221222185600-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022"></span><table class="plainlinks tmbox mbox-small tmbox-notice editrequest" role="presentation" data-origlevel="semi"><tbody><tr><td class="mbox-image"><span typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1d/Information_icon4.svg/30px-Information_icon4.svg.png" decoding="async" width="30" height="30" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1d/Information_icon4.svg/45px-Information_icon4.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1d/Information_icon4.svg/60px-Information_icon4.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="620" data-file-height="620"/></span></span></td><td class="mbox-text">This <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Edit_requests" title="Wikipedia:Edit requests">edit request</a> has been answered. Set the <code style="white-space: nowrap;">|answered=</code> or <code style="white-space: nowrap;">|ans=</code> parameter to <b>no</b> to reactivate your request.</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>If the Palmyrene and Brittanic Emperors are linked to then so should the Gallic Emperors. Include Gallic Emperors by updating the linked to section as follows:
</p>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Gallic_Empire" title="Gallic Empire">Gallic emperors</a> (260-274)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/List_of_Palmyrene_monarchs" title="List of Palmyrene monarchs">Palmyrene emperors</a> (267–273)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Carausian_revolt" title="Carausian revolt">Britannic emperors</a> (286–296)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/List_of_Trapezuntine_emperors" title="List of Trapezuntine emperors">Trapezuntine emperors</a> (1204–1461)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Empire_of_Thessalonica" title="Empire of Thessalonica">Thessalonian emperors</a> (1224–1242)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/List_of_Roman_and_Byzantine_empresses" title="List of Roman and Byzantine empresses">Empresses</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/List_of_Augustae" title="List of Augustae">Augustae</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Roman_usurper" title="Roman usurper">Usurpers</a>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/List_of_Roman_usurpers" title="List of Roman usurpers">Classical</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/List_of_Byzantine_usurpers" title="List of Byzantine usurpers">Eastern</a> <a href="/wiki/Special:Contributions/212.129.85.83" title="Special:Contributions/212.129.85.83">212.129.85.83</a> (<a href="/wiki/User_talk:212.129.85.83" title="User talk:212.129.85.83">talk</a>) 18:56, 22 December 2022 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-212.129.85.83-20221222185600-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20221222185600","author":"212.129.85.83","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-212.129.85.83-20221222185600-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022","replies":["c-Asartea-20221226142200-212.129.85.83-20221222185600"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-212.129.85.83-20221222185600-Semi-protected_edit_request_on_22_December_2022"></span></li></ul></li></ul>
